      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "Faceless Foe",
        "Client": "Scared Researcher",
        "Description": "Gross! There I was, taking a rest,\r\nwhen something wet dripped on\r\nmy shoulder. I look up and\u2014EW!\r\nWrinkles, veins, and\u2014ICK\u2014a pale\r\nmonster with no face that looks\r\nlike a\u2014 *gag* Go hunt it PLEASE!",
